      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Xictequihui para moxehxeloz huan momahmacaz ce tlamantli, quence quemman moxehxeloah ce tlamantli  tlen totlacayo.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
